= astrails-form-builder

1. Copy stylesheets/astrails.css to public/stylesheets (TODO: make rake task)
2. merge css in layout
   stylesheet_link_tag 'application', 'astrails-form', :cache => "main"
3. include ActionView::Helpers::AstrailsFormHelper
4. use astrails_form_for, astrails_fields_for, astrails_form_remote_for instead of original ones

